==Wikipedia dump==
"'''Wild cat'''," in the [[Wikipedia:labor movement]], is a term referring to anything done outside of the control of [[Wikipedia:boss]]es or [[Wikipedia:trade unions]]. A wild cat strike is one without official support or backing. Wild cat activity is often contrasted with normal labour union activity, which is seen as "'''tame cat'''," or "[[Wikipedia:Yellow Dog contract|yellow dog]]."